{"tid":2490805,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"IMF磗家: 同中國切割會令全球經濟受挫 好多國家會跌5%","createTime":"2021-04-16T01:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:43:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9324b65a02c23f558bb0d92c9812f53a5d5db2c5","tid":2490805,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"IMF&rsquo;s Berger Warns China Tech Decoupling Would Slash Global GDP<br />\n<br />\n(Bloomberg) -- A technological decoupling between the U.S. and China and potentially Europe would cut global gross domestic product by an order of magnitude greater than the recent trade war, a senior International Monetary Fund official warned.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The world is such an integrated place,&rdquo; Helge Berger, head of the fund&rsquo;s China mission, said in an interview with Bloomberg Television Friday. &ldquo;If you stop exchanging knowledge across countries or borders you will ultimately pay a price, and this could be fairly high.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nIMF research estimates that technological fragmentation could lead to losses of around 5% of GDP for many countries, or about 10-times the estimated costs of trade tariffs imposed by the U.S. and China.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/imf-s-berger-warns-china-tech-decoupling-would-slash-global-gdp-1.1590984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnnbloomberg.ca%2Fimf-s-berger-warns-china-tech-decoupling-would-slash-global-gdp-1.1590984&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwL6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=6bc5e3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/imf-s-berger-warns-china-tech-decoupling-would-slash-global-gdp-1.1590984</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse